{SOUTH responds 2NT, showing 8+ points with no 5-card suit. 

NORTH only needs to know how many Aces are in the SOUTH hand. He must use Gerber since 
4NT in this situation would not be Blackwood. 

When SOUTH shows two Aces NORTH bids 6NT.}

